{"tid":2172178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《經濟學人》：X聯辦要求學生監視課堂討論，隨時匯報「反動言論」","createTime":"2020-08-24T12:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T13:16:46.000Z","uid":48040,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42ec2d2a85ab16b17b9061be08f8f01ba97b9c1f","tid":2172178,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"《經濟學人》刊登文章《China is killing academic freedom in Hong Kong》提及，有港大學生稱，X聯辦曾經接觸過他，並要求該學生匯報課堂討論情況，以此監察師生言論是否違法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.economist.com/china/2020/08/23/china-is-killing-academic-freedom-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fchina%2F2020%2F08%2F23%2Fchina-is-killing-academic-freedom-in-hong-kong&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbqQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=006f3970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.economist.com/china/2020/08/23/china-is-killing-academic-freedom-in-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，哈佛大學宣布豁免香港學生參與政治敏感話題的討論，以免香港學生可能因違反《國安法》而被起訴。在普林斯頓大學，上中國政治課的學生將在他們的作業上使用代號而不用姓名，以保護他們的身份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296048582089256960?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296048582089256960%3Fs%3D20&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbqQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=322d151c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296048582089256960%3Fs%3D20&h=1b18877b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296048582089256960?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">無論香港或海外大學，都已經成為被監視的地方。學術自由岌岌可危。</span>"},{"pid":"eb820c45c1a04e8338635e8d01e07f89f666f521","tid":2172178,"uid":151313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"真係新疆化"},{"pid":"8dd684425282dcabc92b3b94d67b1de5f4d10e4b","tid":2172178,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"